# kanshi output profile configuration
# =====================================
# Profiles are matched by connected output names (from EDID).
# kanshi activates the first profile whose outputs all match what is plugged in.
#
# To discover output names on a new machine:
#   swaymsg -t get_outputs
#   # or: kanshi --debug (shows matched/unmatched profiles at startup)
#
# Docs: https://sr.ht/~emersion/kanshi/

# -- Home desktop (single DP-3, AMD discrete GPU)
profile desktop {
    output DP-3 mode 2560x1440@165Hz position 0,0 scale 1
}

